OL,3,CHealth fund which provides free
OL,4,Cprescriptions is 'unsustainable'
OL,6,FJersey's Health Insurance Fund (HIF),
OL,7,Fwhich subsidises GP appointments and
OL,8,Fcovers prescription costs for
OL,9,Fresidents, will run out of money
OL,10,Funless action is taken - a new report
OL,11,Fhas concluded.
OL,13,FJersey's Comptroller and Auditor
OL,14,FGeneral (C&AG), Lynn Pamment, says
OL,15,Fthat under current budget plans, this
OL,16,Ffund will run at a deficit for the
OL,17,Fnext four years.
