OL,3,CHealth fund which provides free
OL,4,Cprescriptions is 'unsustainable'
OL,6,FIt means by the end of 2029, there
OL,7,Fwill only be an estimated #62 million
OL,8,Fleft, which will not be enough to
OL,9,Fcover the following year's expected
OL,10,Fcosts.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Ms Pamment adds: "The
OL,13,FHIF is not sustainable in its present
OL,14,Fform and there is no tangible plan for
OL,15,Fprimary care in the context of a
OL,16,Fsustainable, integrated health care
OL,17,Fmodel for the future.
