OL,3,CHealth fund which provides free
OL,4,Cprescriptions is 'unsustainable'
OL,6,F"The Government does not routinely
OL,7,Fassess value for money from new
OL,8,Finitiatives funded from the HIF and
OL,9,Fthe changes since 2022 have increased
OL,10,Fthe risk of overpayment from error or
OL,11,Ffraud."
OL,13,FShe explains that a 2021 review
OL,14,Fhighlighted the fund is not
OL,15,Fsustainable but instead of this being
OL,16,Faddressed, extra benefits were added -
OL,17,Fincreasing the burden.
