OL,6,FIn a statement, it adds: "Ministers
OL,7,Fhave been clear, including in the 2026
OL,8,FBudget, that action is needed to
OL,9,Faddress longterm pressures on health
OL,10,Ffunding caused by increased treatments
OL,11,Fand enhanced support with health care
OL,12,Fcosts.
OL,14,F"Significant preparatory work has
OL,15,Falready taken place, and several of
OL,16,Fthe C&AG findings and recommendations
OL,17,Fare already underway.
