OL,6,F"This includes consideration of reform
OL,7,Fof the Health Insurance Fund as part
OL,8,Fof a whole health care system
OL,9,Fapproach, rather than viewing it in
OL,10,Fisolation."
OL,12,FUnder the current rules, residents who
OL,13,Fhave lived in Jersey for six months or
OL,14,Fmore and paid into the Social Security
OL,15,Fsystem are entitled to a free health
OL,16,Fcard, which grants them access to the
OL,17,FHealth Fund subsidies.
