OL,6,FThese benefits include free
OL,7,Fprescriptions for most medications and
OL,8,F#50.28 towards GP visits in surgeries
OL,9,For at home.
OL,11,FAlthough prices for standard adult
OL,12,Fconsultations with a GP vary across
OL,13,Fdifferent practices, all of those
OL,14,Flisted on the Government website sit
OL,15,Fbelow #50.
OL,17,FFor comparison, Guernsey residents
OL,18,Faged 18 and over are charged between
OL,19,F#72 and #75 for a standard, pay on the
OL,20,Fday GP appointment - including a
OL,21,FStates' contribution of #12.
